      "title": "The number of infected increases significantly",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of confirmed corona infections in the country today (20) has been reported as 75.",
        "It is noteworthy that the number of infected people who were seen in single digits a few weeks ago has increased to more than 50 in the last few days."
